            "link": "https://stackoverflow.com/users/1927205/spqpad",
            "reputation": 130,
            "display_name": "spqpad"
        },
        "content_license": "CC BY-SA 3.0",
        "score": 4,
        "is_accepted": true,
        "last_activity_date": 1422987450,
        "creation_date": 1422987450,
        "body": "<p>Besides the gradle files, AndroidManifest.xml also contains Fabric related data. Make sure to delete this line from the file:<\/p>\n\n<p><code>&lt;meta-data android:name=\"com.crashlytics.ApiKey\" android:value=\"xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx\"/&gt;<\/code><\/p>\n\n<p>Besides this, look for <code>$PROJECT/android/crashlytics.properties<\/code> and remove this as well. This file contains the secret API key.<\/p>\n\n<p>Hope this helps<\/p>\n",
        "answer_id": 28305943,
        "question_id": 28303864
    }],
